{
  "title": "Fresh Spicy Australian Onion Skewers",
  "description": "A light and flavorful Australian dish featuring onions, perfect for a snack or dinner, with a spicy kick and a springy texture, gluten-free-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Australian",
